"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-lifestyle-celeb-news-local-celebs-akani-simbine-possible-bonuses-at-paris-olympics-2024-revealed-tatjana-smith\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.565288550008338, \"rank\": 0.7674843522836841, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbLifestyle\\u00bbCeleb News\\u00bbLocal Celebs\\u00bb'BIG pay day': Akani Simbine's possible bonuses at Paris Olympics revealed  South Africa's 100m sprinter Akani Simbine could earn more than double for a gold medal compared to Tatjana Smith.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.565288550008338, \"rank\": 0.7674843522836841, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 227, \"end\": 240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Akani Simbine\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\"}, {\"begin\": 263, \"end\": 277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 288, \"end\": 300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8410258447463696e-21, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 317, \"end\": 330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Akani Simbine\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's why \\u2026  Thanks to her exploits in the pool at the Paris Olympics 2024, South Africa'sgolden girl Tatjana Smithis set for a lucrative pay day.\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 550, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy the Paris Olympic Games 2024 experience at your favourite ATKV Resort!\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 616, \"end\": 620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"ATKV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATKV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However,Akani Simbinecould earnmore than doublefor a gold medal compared to the celebrated swimmer.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Before the Olympics, theSouth African Sports Confederation and Olympic Committeerevealed their incentive payout structure for athletes and coaches at this year's Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 893, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Sascoc, individual Olympic gold medallists will receiveR400 000for their efforts, while silver and bronze medallists will pocketR200000andR100 000, respectively.\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, the athletes' coaches will also receive their fair share of money for helping produce medalists.\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1195, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Coaches whose athletes win gold at the Olympics will pocket R100 000.\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1266, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Silver and bronze medallist coaches will receive R75 000 and R50 000, respectively.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1316, \"end\": 1319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/R75_(South_Africa)\", \"score\": 0.9634108711086189, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"R75\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/R75_(South_Africa)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/R75_(South_Africa)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, team sports incentives have a one-size-fits-all approach.\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1418, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In disciplines like rugby and relays, gold medallists will take home R100 000 each.\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Conversely, silver medallists will pocket R75 000, while bronze medallists will receive R50 000 per athlete.\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1545, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/R75_(South_Africa)\", \"score\": 0.9634108711086189, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"R75\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/R75_(South_Africa)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/R75_(South_Africa)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, boat-related disciplines will see gold medallists pocketing R200 000 each, with silver and bronzer winners taking home R100 000 and R40 000, respectively.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1754, \"end\": 1757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Renault_R40\", \"score\": 0.999993751522165, \"rank\": 4.578604822336374e-06, \"text\": \"R40\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Renault_R40\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Renault_R40\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, as reported byThe South African website, new Minister of Sport, Arts and Culture,Gayton McKenzie, promised that he has a 'big surprise' for all Team SA medal winners, suggesting there could be more prize money coming their way.\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 2018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1940, \"end\": 1942, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.903433932967238e-28, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With R400 000 already in her pocket, Tatjana Smith might be another R400 000 richer if she secures another gold medal - as expected - in the 200m breaststroke.\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2179, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her win would mean earning R800 000 from the two events.\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, with a single gold medal win, anytrack and field athletewould win over a R1 million despite their gold medal incentives being pegged at R400 000.\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the years, track and field disciplines have become the most watched and followed Olympic events.\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this year,World Athleticsrevealed that starting from the 2024 Paris Olympics, the international federation will award prize money to winners in track and field events.\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2673, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The announcement saw World Athletics become the first international federation to award prize money at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2696, \"end\": 2711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999941209207478, \"rank\": 5.879114043000491e-06, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gold medallists in each of the 48 athletics events in Paris will receive $50 000, which amounts toR916 000.\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2847, \"end\": 2852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999987867341, \"rank\": 1.2131411226866318e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, relay teams will be awarded the same amount to share among team members.\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2983, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Akani Simbine is one of the favourites to win the men's 100m race.\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 3051, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2985, \"end\": 2998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Akani Simbine\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akani_Simbine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If he secures the gold medal, he will pocket at least R1.3 million in incentives from Sascoc and World Athletics.\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3149, \"end\": 3164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999941209207478, \"rank\": 5.879114043000491e-06, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's before any possible pay day for the men's 4x100m relay.\", \"from\": 3167, \"to\": 3233, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the latest Paris Olympics 2024 news, bookmarkThe South African website'sdedicated section for free-to-read content  WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3355, \"end\": 3358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.9999999455581033, \"rank\": 5.425423020454155e-08, \"text\": \"WIN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\"}, {\"begin\": 3359, \"end\": 3361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"score\": 0.9996668351380381, \"rank\": 0.0003277020312350802, \"text\": \"R2\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DVD_region_code\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Freelance writing positions available  Follow The South African on Facebook for the latest local and international news  Follow The South African's WhatsApp channel for the latest sport, lifestyle and local news  Follow The South African on X for the latest, breaking news  A brand new shopping mall is coming to Pretoria East, bringing major retailers and new convenience to the area.\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3583, \"end\": 3591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9998631972299493, \"rank\": 0.0001368214876441327, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Orlando Pirates are reportedly set to welcome a new staff member i